  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    A simple coordinate class for representing locations.
    CountdownTimer
    The timer used for starting games.
    Debug
    A simple class for debugging that relies on skater77i's DebugAPI
    DragonGame
    The main class for a minigame.
    EventListeners
    Most event listeners in this plugin are here.
    GameBlock
    A block which is part of a GameMap.
    GameLifecycle
    The "lifecycle" for the game.
    GameMap
    A map that can be resetted and has a Queue.
    Main
    The main class of DragonGameCore.
    PlaceholderHook
    The class that implements PlaceholderAPI integration.
    Queue
    A queue for a game, which is map-specific.
    Team
    A team, which is map-specific.
    Wrapper
    A class for many random methods that are somewhat associated with games or maps.
